race.description: 2025 Cadillac Racing Spring Classic Special Event
race.comment: COMPTON GYPSY (7) could not have been more impressive last start in her scintillating 29.41 win at this track over 512m. Expected to go close again if runs up to latest time. CAPYBARA (4) is progressing well and looks close to another win after hitting the frame last run (29.50) at this track. Solid record at the distance winning three races. The form from her last run stacks up well. Expected to be in this for a long way. LEKTRA BETA (3) was in the placings last time but prior to that he posted a blistering 23.16 win over 410m at Horsham. Top win two back and can measure up again. LEKTRA UNHINGED (1) was in the money again last start when third at this track (29.64).
